title: AUTOCAD 2009
description:
With AutoCAD software, Autodesk has just one goal in mind: increasing 
 your productivity. AutoCAD 2009 boosts efficiency with customizable    
 and extensible user interface enhancements that increase overall       
 drafting productivity by decreasing the number of steps needed to      
 reach a command. Newly designed, innovative features simplify working  
 with layers and help make new users productive as quickly as possible. 
 Easy-to-use navigation tools make finding your way around 3D models    
 a snap. Move to new highs of productivity with AutoCAD software.
